						<summary>

						<p>This records a gift of land as <hi rend="italic">dēvadāna</hi> to the temple of Tirumāṇiyūṟal-nāyanār at Muḻibil (Mogili) by a merchant named Niyamaṅkiḻār-chakravarttigaḷ. He is stated have reclaimed the land for cultivation.</p>						

